gov.nasa.gsfc.hessi.jidl.prep.client.bridge
Class VxoPrepClient

java.lang.Object
  gov.nasa.gsfc.hessi.jidl.prep.client.bridge.VxoPrepClient
All Implemented Interfaces:
com.idl.javaidl.JIDLOutputListener
public class VxoPrepClient
extends java.lang.Object
implements com.idl.javaidl.JIDLOutputListener

This class bridges between IDL and the WSDL auto-generated stub classed generated with the help of the Java Web Toolkit (Jaxws 2.1.4). The WSDL is loaded from the PrepServer directly http://wilco.gsfc.nasa.gov:8080/VxoPrepServer/vxoprep?wsdl This client can be used dependent or independent from IDL!

Since:
Revision 19
Author:
Laszlo Istvan Etesi
